descriptionText: This ORIENT 48mm quartz sports watch showcases a stainless steel case and band with a black dial and bezel. Distinguished features include a seconds sub-dial, 12-hour sub-dial, an additional time-tracking sub-dial, a convenient date aperture, and luminescent hands and hour markers. The TT0Y002B has a screw-down crown to ensure water resistance of 100 meters.

This ORIENT 48mm quartz sports watch showcases a stainless steel case and band with a white dial and black bezel. Distinguished features include a seconds sub-dial, 12-hour sub-dial, an additional time-tracking sub-dial, a convenient date aperture, a black chapter ring, and luminescent hands and hour markers. The TT0Y003W has a screw-down crown to ensure water resistance of 100 meters.

The model features three hands and date display, and a large 42.4 mm case, having chronograph functions shown on the sub dials at 6 and 9 o’clock for increased legibility. Incorporating a vintage feel, the model comes in a green dial with a nylon strap. This flight style chronograph models exude practicality and clarity with aviation design accents.

This ORIENT 43mm quartz sports watch features a stainless steel case and rubber band with a white dial, black unidirectional rotating bezel, blue chapter ring, and convenient date aperture. Luminescent hands outlined in gray and gray hour markers complete the watch’s adventurous allure. The sporty UG1X008B supports water resistance of 50 meters.

This ORIENT 43.9mm quartz sports watch showcases a stainless steel case, black dial, and black rubber band with red lining. Red sub-dials and numberings along the chapter ring enhance the watch’s adventurous appeal. The sporty KV00005B supports water resistance of 50 meters.
